<view class="page">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="title">CodexBridge 部署助手</view>
    <view class="subtitle">给已有 Codex 用户，把微信桥接部署步骤压到一条 command。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">系统</view>
    <view class="segmented">
      <button
        wx:for="{{platforms}}"
        wx:key="id"
        class="segment {{selectedPlatform === item.id ? 'active' : ''}}"
        data-id="{{item.id}}"
        bindtap="selectPlatform"
      >{{item.label}}</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">部署命令</view>
    <view class="command">{{command}}</view>
    <view class="actions">
      <button class="primary" bindtap="copyCommand">复制命令</button>
      <button class="secondary" bindtap="copyLocalCommand">复制本地测试命令</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">流程 check</view>
    <view class="checklist">
      <view class="check-item" wx:for="{{steps}}" wx:key="title">
        <view class="dot">{{index + 1}}</view>
        <view class="check-copy">
          <view class="check-title">{{item.title}}</view>
          <view class="check-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section warning">
    <view class="section-title">注意</view>
    <view class="note">小程序不能直接控制用户电脑。真正的安装动作必须由用户在本机终端运行 installer。</view>
    <view class="note">个人微信桥接不是 OpenAI 官方能力，适合先用小号 test。</view>
  </view>
</view>
